&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;strong&gt; Scrub Nurses &amp; ODP’s&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for Theatre Practitioners and Health Care Support Workers to join our team based at Grantham.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and motivated team players to join our friendly operating theatre department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are offering positions in either scrub, anaesthetic or circulatory roles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will support learning and development and encourage skill mixing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently a green site providing a 7 day service. We deliver a range of surgical specialities within our 6 theatres including Breast, Gynae, General Surgery, ENT, Urology and Orthopaedics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Lizzie Saxby&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Theatre Sister&lt;/p&gt;
